            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# SuperScreenshot 0.9.84

- 修复从截图区域外侧接近边框时缩放光标难以触发。
- 边框内外各约 20px 均可进行调整。
- 使用全局坐标主动判定缩放方向，并避免遮挡工具栏。

---

- Fixed resize cursor detection when approaching from outside the capture area.
- Supports resizing within about 20px on either side of each border.
- Uses direction-independent global pointer detection without blocking the toolbar.
]]></description>
